shing site, then you can steal the private key of the victim. Perhaps you can upload js to the site, but I could not do it.","weakness":{"id":60,"name":"Cross-site Scripting (XSS) - Generic"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":271626,"file_name":"hh.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/271/626/83ef354f76a3259a85993097383e7c77ac46f6d7/hh.png?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22hh.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27hh.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQYTWDFFHY%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T095851Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIQCsQkXn7X9PO2iJt3qpEjQMg1QJl04XwkvVDws8JRf%2BNgIgOHjCpJJC%2FOwuWT15VhGioNYvyHF5sPUSWHlXXcLsgLYqugUI8f%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARADGgwwMTM2MTkyNzQ4NDkiDKejxffXxbjtN50cKyqOBS1hwjhbOaPkuasgdKdOvPUAe1RypVJpC%2Fn1wy81vwEKnEtUuvec1ohXhAGVxvtg8QasMpfvmMKMwVFMvOEHrnUHJhnwJWkIYzvvqZlh3F%2F%2ByoT8NG9y14qs0IlmUXBWPyQvnjAJeuhu3C4e0uhIrmcAt0Q5HdXvh%2FK091ORj%2BLxtOvcT1bbpNWJDJx%2BuWgVhQnPnLHJaHdF9uO74UFt0fsxnkMaeNkEh4E2ZEG5VDuMyifpQnT%2BY%2BMugGOqPyCGYv8ZSZ3oMARyCHRPjKo1wwVo5TtCQk56fR8a6C%2B%2F8VNyRmGanLffzn83RdbbuIS6rMlJuPnnv2PzuJfbPg5NqNxwzbZR2WokQQln83ex4m61IH9xG%2FNtZCAMNCZrLabw2mb3kgu6PZW7W%2Bm5m6hlCoHZDIG3wD%2FbwUPFVqq2Gi%2Be5NHjqnl77a0voOKFALwSpp1TcS5FoMuT%2F%2BQXmHinqd3lvmu3jqPigJP%2F%2FfPDj6qRJZsdjB3WApLtyEcYMqpcEflUda8cEryIs%2Fcp0aEBbYhAjnJ04AwJUT1%2FMJQSrP5SXmzbcutoX8qtmcFjH5o2fUldyZnVHofjJdN9mhotyCr62d%2Fi2wwCy7KA6MM0%2FWTlELszcLDdLZLuz6GIYiFWgxGSX8C%2BloOKqjemULWg5TZvorK1YKwqkYOpLa9E51MYtx3ujWicQ1cwUceh2pYhZvmaN1KlX4%2BPgWjO6tq7NwEIThOEK7Dq%2FqB0Yt7V2oU1qK6tS8Y1O9bcrvmF4SCWO95VZQ8w7EaDodX5CTvh%2BWgFLKW2qkECWj8Md73rURv5oe8SmL55He9D%2Bn3ZQ3ulRaRyaqXUBaqwYouNh6F1sybb8cdimFAlafjSanswUzCT7sbPBjqxAZyQ0Qid4CZHtWSNIdIg1hxb0QTWM93ORagk%2FBMlesCn